io.sphere.sdk.reviews.commands

Interface ReviewCreateCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Command<Review>, CreateCommand<Review>, MetaModelExpansionDsl<Review,ReviewCreateCommand,ReviewExpansionModel<Review>>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<Review,ReviewCreateCommand>, ReferenceExpansionSupport<Review>, SphereRequest<Review>

    public interface ReviewCreateCommand
extends CreateCommand<Review>, MetaModelExpansionDsl<Review,ReviewCreateCommand,ReviewExpansionModel<Review>>
    Creates a review. 
    withProduct(client(), product ->
    withCustomer(client(), customer -> {
        final ReviewDraft reviewDraft = ReviewDraftBuilder.of(product, customer)
                .authorName("John Smith")
                .title("It is ok")
                .text("This product is ok.")
                .score(0.36)
                .build();
        final Review review = execute(ReviewCreateCommand.of(reviewDraft));
        assertThat(review.getAuthorName()).contains("John Smith");
        assertThat(review.getTitle()).contains("It is ok");
        assertThat(review.getText()).contains("This product is ok.");
        assertThat(review.getScore()).isEqualTo(0.36, within(0.1));
    })
);

    See the test code.
